OL,3,CRare technical breakdown on BBC One
OL,5,FBBC London remained on its closing
OL,6,Fshot until an apology caption
OL,7,Fappeared on the network feed.
OL,9,FWithin 15 seconds of the appearance
OL,10,Fof the apology message, normal
OL,11,Fservice was resumed.
OL,13,FViewers of BBC One Northern Ireland
OL,14,Fwere oblivious to the fault, as the
OL,15,Fearly evening national weather is not
OL,16,Fbroadcast there. Instead, a quick
OL,17,Fnational weather update is
OL,18,Fincorporated into the local weather
OL,19,Fbulletin.
