OL,3,CRare technical breakdown on BBC One
OL,5,FIn Scotland, about 10 seconds of
OL,6,Fblack and silence was broadcast
OL,7,Fimmediately after BBC Reporting
OL,8,FScotland. The BBC One Scotland
OL,9,Fapology graphic then appeared. The
OL,10,Fannouncer provided a quick verbal
OL,11,Fapology.
OL,13,FThings returned to normal just under
OL,14,Fa minute-and-a-half later.
OL,16,FBBC One Wales broadcast just over a
OL,17,Fminute of black and silence before
OL,18,Ftheir apology graphic appeared. The
OL,19,Fchannel was back on track about 20
OL,20,Fseconds later.
